{"id": "jos021", "name": "Cam_Cafe_697_08_19", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_Piano_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Good stuff. Exactly the same as the one Saxon made.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "You seem to be very cautious towards me.\nPlease, relax. I'm one of your uncle's old friends as well.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "I've never seen you before.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Your uncle wasn't exactly welcoming to me... Our ideals are a bit... different. However, he's a great man. He dedicated his entire life for all of us. He deserves all the respect he got.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "But Boss Luo and other are...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Yes, the top members of the Ando gang getting arrested has made everyone very nervous. I have a meeting with a few old friends later today.\n... However, I feel like the talk with you deserves priority, so I came here first.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "With me...? I was the one who f***ed up and got Boss Luo and Co. busted... The thing uncle's been carefully maintaining...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Balance, right?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... Yes.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Saxon did a lot of things for everyone. The three gangs benefited greatly from him and were able to thrive together. Despite our differences, I also hold a deep respect for your uncle.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "However, JOE, an opportunity now rests in your hands... one that allows both us and the entire gang business to take a big step forward.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "A big step forward?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "The Ando gang is now in disarray. This very night, the Baro Brotherhood is the biggest organization still operating. So, naturally, we have to do something for everyone. To do so, we need to prepare a large amount of resources and information... a lot more than anything in the past.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Umm, and then?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "I feel like you should realize this as well... Why do you think I specifically made the trip here?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Aren't you here for a drink?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Indeed, for this \"Martini\".\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... OH! You mean this!\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "JOEZ Cafe's ability to collect resources and information surpasses that of the three gangs combined. When Saxon was still alive, he only allowed transactions in the grey area... but now, we have even more options.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "But pops did that because...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "To maintain the balance between the gangs. That's why he didn't get involved with illegal businesses. I know.\n... Yet the balance no longer exists anymore.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Umm...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "JOE, the gangs are facing a very tough situation. However, a crisis is also an opportunity. As long as you work with me, not only can we recreate the glory days, but we can also receive even greater benefits... you, me, every gang organization in Node 08, all of us.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "I... get benefits as well?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "... Certainly. \nIn the past, the price of this Martini is ten percent of the transaction amount, correct?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Yes. A price set by pops. Hasn't changed in decades.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "I give you double.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "If you agree to lift the limitations, for future Baro Brotherhood transactions, you get twenty percent. What do you think?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Don't pull a long face. I'm asking you a question.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "... Twenty-five.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "... What?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "I want one-fourth of the transaction amount...!\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "image", "attrs": ["jos2101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Hoho... hahaha! Boy! I knew you wouldn't disappoint me!\nAlright! One-fourth it is!\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "To celebrate our future partnership, a toast?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Of course! I'm beginning to like you even more, boy!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cheers", "Cheers"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "Arooo...\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_Piano_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "良い酒だ。Saxonの酒そっくりだな。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "私を警戒しているようだな。\nその必要はない。\n私もお前の叔父さんの古い知人だ。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "あんたに会ったことがない。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "お前の叔父さんは私をあまり歓迎していなかった……\n互いの考え方に差異があってな。\nだが、あいつはその一生を我々に捧げていた。\n尊敬に値する。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "でもLuo兄貴たちが……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "そうだ。アンドーの主要メンバーが逮捕され、我々の内部も穏やかでない。\n私も、この後友人たちと話し合いをせねばならない。\n……だが、君と話をする方が重要だと私は判断した。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "俺と……？\n俺のせいでLuo兄貴たちが捕まっちまった……\n叔父がずっと守ってきた……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "「均衡」か？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……あぁ。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Saxonは皆のためにと動いてきた。\n我々三大勢力も、おかげさまで共存共栄してこれた。\n私も彼のことは尊敬している。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "だが、JOEよ。\nお前は、今、我々とお前自身がさらに一歩前進するための運命をその手に握っている……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "一歩前進……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "アンドーは今、群龍無首の状態だ。\n今晩からは、バローが最大の組織となる。\nそうなれば、我々は皆のために多少の努力をするのが当然だろう？\nそのためには、大量の物資と情報を用意しなくてはならない……これまでよりもずっと多くのな。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "あー…それで？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "分からないか？\nなぜ、私がわざわざここまで足を運んだと思う？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "酒を飲みに来たんじゃ？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "そうだ。この「マティーニ」を飲みに来た。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……あぁ！\nこれのことか！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "JOEZ Cafeの物資や、情報収集能力は、我々三大勢力をもしのぐものがある。\nSaxonがいた頃は、グレーゾーンの取引にのみ着手してきたようだが……これからは、より多くの取引に着手するべきだろう。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "でも、親父は……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "勢力間の均衡を保つため、違法行為には手を出さない。\nそれは知っている。\n……だが、均衡などとうの昔に崩れているのだよ。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "え……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "JOE、我々は今厳しい局面を迎えている。だが、これは転機でもある。\n君が、我々に手を貸してくれさえすれば、我々は共に栄誉を取り戻し、これまで以上の利益を手にすることができるだろう。\n……君も、私も、Node08の組織全てがだ。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "俺にも……？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……当然だ。\nこのマティーニの価格は、取引額の1割だったか？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "親父がそう決めた……\n10年間変わったことはない。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "ならば、その倍だ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "制限を緩めると約束すれば、今後バロー会が関わる取引における報酬を2割にしよう。\nどうだ？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "なんだその顔は。\nお前に聞いてるんだぞ。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……2.5。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……なに？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "報酬は4分の1だ……！\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "image", "attrs": ["jos2101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "フッ…クックック…ハハハハハ！\n面白い！私の目は間違っていなかったようだ！\n分かった！4分の1で手を打とう。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "今後の仕事に乾杯しますか！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "よし！気に入った！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cheers", "乾杯"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "ワゥゥ……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_Piano_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "好酒，和 Saxon 調的一模一樣。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "你似乎對我戒心很重。\n不需要這樣，我也是你舅舅的舊識。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我從來沒看過你。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "你舅舅不太歡迎我……想法有點差異，但他是個好人，將一生奉獻給我們大家，值得尊敬。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "可是 Luo 大哥他們……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "對，Ando 幫重要成員被捕，大夥都很緊張，我等等還得和幾個老朋友開個會。\n……不過我覺得，先和你聊聊比較重要。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "和我……？我害 Luo 大哥他們被抓了……舅舅一直小心翼翼地維持……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "「平衡」嗎？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Saxon 為大家做了很多事，三大幫派都因此受益，才能共存共榮。我對你舅舅也是非常景仰的。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "但 JOE 啊，現在有個機會正掌握在你手裡……可以讓我們彼此、整個黑幫勢力都更進一步。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "更進一步？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Ando 幫群龍無首，就在今晚，Baro 兄弟會已是現存最大的組織，當然要為大家出一份力。為此，得準備大量的物資與情報……遠超過去所需。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "呃，然後呢？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "我覺得你應該想得到才對……你覺得我為什麼會特地跑來這裡？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "不是來喝酒的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "是啊，喝「這杯」馬丁尼。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……喔，你指的是這個！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "JOEZ Cafe 的物資、情報收集能力，比我們三個組織加起來更強。Saxon 在世時，只開放遊走於灰色地帶生意……但現在，我們可以有更多選擇。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "但老爹是為了……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "維護勢力平衡，才不碰非法生意，我知道。\n……但平衡早已不復存在了。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "呃……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "JOE，黑幫正面臨嚴苛的局面，但危機也是轉機。只要你和我合作，我們不僅能再現榮景，還能獲得更大的利益……你、我、全 Node 08 的組織都是。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我……也有好處？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……當然。\n以往，這杯馬丁尼的價格是交易額的一成，對嗎？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "嗯，老爹訂的價，幾十年來從沒變過。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "我給你翻倍。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "只要你答應放寬限制，往後我們 Baro 兄弟會的案子，你可以拿兩成。怎麼樣？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "別愁眉苦臉的啊，我在問你問題呢。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……二點五。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……什麼？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我要抽四分之一……！\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "image", "attrs": ["jos2101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "呵呵……哈哈哈！小子！我果然沒看錯你！好！就四分之一！\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "為了今後合作愉快，來乾一杯？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "當然！我越來越喜歡你了，小子！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cheers", "乾杯"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "汪嗚……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_Piano_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "좋은 술이군. 예전에 Saxon이 만들어줬던 거랑 똑같은 맛이야.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "아직도 나를 엄청나게 경계하고 있는 것 같은데... 그럴 필요 없다. 나 역시 네 삼촌과 오래 알고 지낸 사이니깐.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "난 당신을 한 번도 본 적이 없어.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "네 삼촌이 날 별로 반기질 않았거든...... 뭐 단순한 생각의 차이랄까? 물론 그 사람은 좋은 사람이지. 나도 알고 있다고. 일생동안 우리 모두를 위해 얼마나 헌신했는지도. 존경받아 마땅할 인물이지.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "하지만 Luo형님이……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "그래. Ando파의 핵심 인물들이 대부분 체포되었지. 때문에 지금 모두가 초긴장 상태이고 말이야. 그래서 조금 이따가 다른 '오랜 친구들'과도 이 문제에 대해 얘기를 나누러 가야만 하지..... 하지만, 너와 먼저 얘기를 나누는 것이 더 중요하다고 판단했다.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "나와……? \n나 때문에 Luo 형님들이  붙잡혔어…  영감이 계속 유지하려고 했던……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "「균형」...말인가?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……응.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Saxon은 3대 조직을 위해 엄청나게 많은 일들을 했고 덕분에 모두가 공존하며 번창해 나갈 수 있었지. 나 역시 네 삼촌을 매우 존경하고 있고 말이야.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "하지만 JOE.\n ...우리와 같은 모든 조직 세력들이 한 단계 진보할 수 있는 기회가 지금 네 손에 달려있다.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "...진보라고?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Ando파는 현재 머리를 잃은 상황이야. 오늘 밤으로 Baro파는 현존하는 조직들 중 가장 큰 세력이 되었다. 따라서 우리도 모두를 위해 뭔가를 해야만 하는 의무가 생긴 셈이지.물론 그걸 위해선 더 많은 정보와 물자도 필요하고 말이야...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "아... 그리고?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "그 다음은 너도 알고 있을 텐데?\n넌 내가 왜 굳이 이곳으로 와서 널 찾았을 거라고 생각하나?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "술마시러 온 거겠지.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "그래. 「마티니」를 마시러 온 거지.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……아... 그런 뜻이었군!\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "JOEZ Cafe의 물자와 정보 수집 능력은 우리 3대 조직의 힘을 합한 것보다 훨씬 뛰어나다. Saxon이 살아있을 땐 그저 회색 지대 범위 안에서만 거래를 할 수 있지... 하지만 지금은.... 더 많은 선택지가 놓여있다.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "하지만 영감은....\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "세력의 균형을 위해 불법적인 거래는 취급하지 않았지. 나도 알고 있다.... 하지만 균형은 이미 무너져버렸어.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "음……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "JOE. 현재 조직들은 모두 냉혹한 국면에 처해있다. 하지만 위기는 또 다른 기회이기도 하지. 너가 우리에게 손을 빌려주면 우리는 다시 영광을 되찾고 지금 이상의 이익을 손에 쥘 수 있을 거다..... 너, 나, 그리고 Node 08의 모든 조직들이 말이지.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "나도 포함되는 건가?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……물론이지.\n이 마티니의 가격은 본래 거래액의 1할로 책정되있지?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "영감이 정한 가격이야. \n10년 동안 한 번도 변동된 적이 없었지.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "두 배를 주지.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "네가 제한을 풀어주겠다고 약속만 한다면, 이후 우리 Baro파가 얻게되는 거래에서 2할을 네게 주도록 하지. 어떤가?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "그런 표정 짓지 말라고.\n그냥 의견을 물어본 것 뿐이니.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……2.5.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "……뭐?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "내 몫은 4분의 1이다.....!\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "image", "attrs": ["jos2101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "흐...크흐흐......크하하하하하하하!\n애송이! 역시 내눈은 틀리지 않았어! \n알겠다! 네 몫은 4분의 1로 하지!\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "우리의 협업을 기원하며, 한 잔 어때?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "물론! 갈수록 네가 마음에 드는군!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Cheers", "건배"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Zark"], "content": "크르르르……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["JOEZ_Cafe_Piano_BGM"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "好酒，和 Saxon 調的一模一樣。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "你似乎對我戒心很重。\n不需要這樣，我也是你舅舅的舊識。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我從來沒看過你。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "你舅舅不太歡迎我……想法有點差異，但他是個好人，將一生奉獻給我們大家，值得尊敬。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "可是 Luo 大哥他們……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "對，Ando 幫重要成員被捕，大夥都很緊張，我等等還得和幾個老朋友開個會。\n……不過我覺得，先和你聊聊比較重要。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "和我……？我害 Luo 大哥他們被抓了……舅舅一直小心翼翼地維持……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "「平衡」嗎？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……嗯。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Saxon 為大家做了很多事，三大幫派都因此受益，才能共存共榮。我對你舅舅也是非常景仰的。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "但 JOE 啊，現在有個機會正掌握在你手裡……可以讓我們彼此、整個黑幫勢力都更進一步。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "更進一步？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Ando 幫群龍無首，就在今晚，Baro 兄弟會已是現存最大的組織，當然要為大家出一份力。為此，得準備大量的物資與情報……遠超過去所需。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "呃，然後呢？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "我覺得你應該想得到才對……你覺得我為什麼會特地跑來這裡？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "不是來喝酒的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "是啊，喝「這杯」馬丁尼。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "……喔，你指的是這個！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "JOEZ Cafe 的物資、情報收集能力，比我們三個組織加起來更強。Saxon 在世時，只開放遊走於灰色地帶生意……但現在，我們可以有更多選擇。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "但老爹是為了……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "維護勢力平衡，才不碰非法生意，我知道。\n……但平衡早已不復存在了。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "呃……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "JOE，黑幫正面臨嚴苛的局面，但危機也是轉機。只要你和我合作，我們不僅能再現榮景，還能獲得更大的利益……你、我、全 Node 08 的組織都是。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我……也有好處